  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-v/section-521"
             temporalId="sSection 521">
      <num>Section 521</num>
      <heading>Amendment of ordinances</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The amendment of any section or sections of an ordinance may be accomplished solely
               by the re-enactment of such section or sections at length, as amended.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
